{"tid":2165114,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[ViuTV] 今晚瞓酒店 逢星期一至五23:00 準時CHECK IN(5)","createTime":"2020-08-19T15:11:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T15:27:52.000Z","uid":31098,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f0837849074db0e58800e9578d366459440ba7d2","tid":2165114,"uid":31098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T15:11:06.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\">今晚瞓酒店 豉油王炒麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wE7W1ET.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwE7W1ET.gif&h=e0004bf3&s={SIZE}\" /></span><br />\n《今晚瞓酒店》<br />\nch.99 ViuTV 星期一至五晚 11:00</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.viu.tv/encore/staycation\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.viu.tv%2Fencore%2Fstaycation&d=MESMej01p5OZpZHaxDRufVtf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=ba51575f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.viu.tv/encore/staycation</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.viu.tv/resized-1280/shares/vod_images/vi_voddrama_series_desc_t/202008/zh_tw/original_horizontal/s202008030112164.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.viu.tv%2Fresized-1280%2Fshares%2Fvod_images%2Fvi_voddrama_series_desc_t%2F202008%2Fzh_tw%2Foriginal_horizontal%2Fs202008030112164.jpg&h=2773fc7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"small\">疫情持續，全球旅遊業停頓，最中意去旅行的香港人無得飛，無得 「梳乎」，個個叫苦連天。正一「有假冇埞去，有錢冇埞使」，你話點算好? <br />\n一連十集的 《今晚瞓酒店》，將會帶 大家嘆盡全港又靚又有特色的酒店。例如坐擁infinity pool、盡覽維港180度壯闊海景的香港維港凱悅尚萃酒店；由百年古蹟改建而成的大澳文物酒店；吸引兩岸三地網紅帶齊 睡衣、玫瑰花等道具來打卡的天后The TUVE等。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ViuTV.hk/videos/2973872982742168/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FViuTV.hk%2Fvideos%2F2973872982742168%2F&d=MESMej01p5OZpZHaxDRufVtf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=3000a01a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ViuTV.hk/videos/2973872982742168/</a><br />\n由Edan、Dixon、 Emily、林婷帶領，發掘香港至靚酒店打卡位，CHILL住過每一個晚上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無得去旅行，無得住酒店，都有得睇定bookmark先！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>10／8日起星期一至五晚11點！下星期一晚準時CHECK IN！<br />\n#今晚瞓酒店</strong></p>"},{"pid":"ca0cf079f145434954f390cd80b2a0aac8526541","tid":2165114,"uid":119591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T15:12:38.000Z","msg":"最尾兩集林婷會唔會出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac482314d95de04d5b2c8f78fb35b8688b27ecbc","tid":2165114,"uid":30294,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T15:12:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ee44e94e370fa7fb12eac3de7576986216b7817","tid":2165114,"uid":33798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T15:12:48.000Z","msg":"灣仔算多野行，乜都有咁"},{"pid":"1a60223368998c608d7c853c5bc55817eedce1ad","tid":2165114,"uid":200663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T15:13:02.000Z","msg":"Dixon <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcf656ae1fb793d6888199c3649832fc8c6cff68","tid":2165114,"uid":31098,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T15:13:17.000Z","msg":"有人開咗，推嗰個啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[ViuTV] 今晚瞓酒店 逢星期一至五23:00 準時CHECK IN (5)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2158116\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2158116</a>"},{"pid":"3cbcae3f3b1c2249d5fd7c6d711155179964c5f7","tid":2165114,"uid":151760,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T